    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Notification of tobacco or herbal products for smoking
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance for businesses needing to notify the government that they are placing a tobacco or herbal smoking product on the market.</p>

  </div>
</div>

